snippet.title: Doom Zero trailer (and celebrating 25 years of Doom II)
snippet.description:
2 years in the making, Doom Zero will release on the 30th Sep 2019 which is also the 25th anniversary of Doom II, released way back on the 30th Sep 1994.
For more info and a link to the download, head over to https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/109216-doom-zero-launch-and-celebrating-25-years-of-doom-ii/
or
https://www.moddb.com/mods/doom-zero

You can also download the HQ modified music tracks here:
https://mega.nz/file/kM9lnBra#bo8Wkuyan1lBVBL3EZX3yOnDKz_bO2isTz-xH-euGfc
